@HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### 开发测试 Token
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/dev-token
Accept: application/json

### 获取 Todo 列表（替换 Token）
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/todos
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
Accept: application/json

### 创建 Todo
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/todos
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试任务",
  "description": "这是一个测试",
  "priority": 1
}

### 更新 Todo
PATCH {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/todos/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

### 删除 Todo
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/todos/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>

### 获取用户信息
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
